---
title: Cheesy Chorizo & Chicken Breast Pizza Inspired Pasta Bake with Spinach and Garlic Ciabatta
description: This Cheesy Chorizo & Chicken Breast Pizza Inspired Pasta Bake is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W47_UK_F14691-5_Main_low-c5c53894.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/650c2c45d19550681e3ba3d1.pdf
